# Checklist

**Usage:** This file contains pre-flight checks, validation criteria, and quality standards for this skill. Use it to verify outputs and maintain quality standards.

---

## Pre-Execution Checklist

Before starting the main work, verify:

### Environment

- [ ] Required tools are available
- [ ] Input files exist and are readable
- [ ] Output directory is writable
- [ ] Configuration is valid

### Input Validation

- [ ] Input data is properly formatted
- [ ] Required fields are present
- [ ] No conflicting parameters
- [ ] Values are within acceptable ranges

### Prerequisites

- [ ] Dependencies are installed
- [ ] External services are accessible
- [ ] Required permissions are granted
- [ ] Resource limits are acceptable

