## Post-Execution Checklist

After completing the work, verify:

### Output Verification

- [ ] All expected outputs were generated
- [ ] Output files are valid and complete
- [ ] No errors or warnings in logs
- [ ] File sizes are reasonable

### Quality Checks

- [ ] Results meet quality criteria
- [ ] No data corruption
- [ ] Consistent with input
- [ ] Meets performance expectations

### Cleanup

- [ ] Temporary files removed
- [ ] Resources released
- [ ] Logs archived (if needed)
- [ ] State reset for next run

---

## Sign-Off Criteria

The work is complete when:

✅ **Mandatory:**
- [ ] All pre-execution checks pass
- [ ] All validation steps pass
- [ ] All post-execution checks pass
- [ ] No critical errors

✅ **Quality:**
- [ ] Output meets all quality criteria
- [ ] Performance within acceptable range
- [ ] No unresolved warnings

✅ **Documentation:**
- [ ] Changes documented (if applicable)
- [ ] Results logged
- [ ] Known issues noted

